-- Eskom Expecting Tariff Increases After 2013 to Be at Similar Levels to Now
-- B y   R o n   D e r b y
-- 2010-09-29T08:22:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-29/eskom-expecting-tariff-increases-after-2013-to-be-at-similar-levels-to-now.html
Eskom Holdings Ltd. expects
increases in the tariffs it charges power users after 2013 to be
at “similar levels” to the ones recently-granted by the
National Energy Regulator of South Africa, the utility’s General
Manager of Sales, Algie Kiewiets, said in a presentation in
Johannesburg today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ron Derby in Johannesburg at 
